Name: [Affinity] Like a Fish in Water
Desc: Qingyi has evoked the Mindscape: <color=#FFAF2C>[Insulation Breakdown]</color>. After launching a Dash Attack or Dodge Counter, your character can <color=#2BAD00>immediately follow up with</color> certain attacks near the end of the Basic Attack combo.
Desc2: Qingyi has achieved her daily water intake goal, and she is in her optimal state for the day.
